Package com.fluidops.iwb.mapping

Simple mapping framework.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    AlignmentOperator
    interface that helps providers to either generate owl:sameAs or align URIs before entering data into the triplestore the API is inspired by the SILK Link specification language: http://www4.wiwiss.fu-berlin.de/bizer/silk/spec/ It usually defines 2 datasources: source: the IWB repository target: the provider graph passed on as a List of Statements LinkCondition: currently simplified to a Pair of predicate URIs.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Align
    helper methods to align mapped resources to resources existing in the current DB
    Bean
    jsp bean used for the mapping UI prototype.
    Data
    base class for all mapping data models such as tree, table, graph, pojos, etc.
    GraphData
    simple graph data model.
    PojoData
    pojo datamodel.
    PredicateAlignmentOperator  
    RdfData
    RDF data model.
    StringData
    raw string data
    TableData
    table datamodel.
    TreeData
    XML Tree data model
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    TableData.PropertyType
    Column types for the underlying table, used when translating to RDF

Package com.fluidops.iwb.mapping Description

Simple mapping framework. Can assemble a pipeline which converts inputs to RDF. Intermediate formats can be trees, tables, pojos, graphs
